Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow the two sides are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,even!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This... this can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:31.44,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Even?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:32.70,Thinking,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:34.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's just by a little, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Meijin is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Only Yose is left...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:22.75,Thinking,,0,0,0,,When I read the game out to the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.42,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.09,Thinking,,0,0,0,,myself losing by a half moku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:34.78,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Unlike all the other conflicts on the board, there\Nis only one path you can take for Yose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:40.27,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Though it's difficult to play right,\Nand easy to stray away from...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.75,Thinking,,0,0,0,,there is only one correct path to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:47.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He won't make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:53.68,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He probably sees the final board just like I do.
