Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He resigned!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Touya resigned here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai has...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,won!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why resign!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only Yose left, but it's very close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He read the game till the end already!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But they still have to fight over kos...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he serious!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Touya resigned here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the Meijin has played\Ncalmly and rationally...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai still played above him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That move he made...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and the moves that followed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:18:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there... no way for the Meijin\Nto turn the game around!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No... there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:15.16,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's the old...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:16.76,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:20.84,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I've come upon an answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:26.51,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The old Shindou is the person I see inside Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:29.25,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:33.05,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This doesn't answer any questions though...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:51.94,Sai,,0,0,0,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:54.36,Sai,,0,0,0,,Touya Kouyou...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.37,Sai,,0,0,0,,You responded to me exceedingly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:19:00.37,Sai,,0,0,0,,Each of your brilliant moves...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:04.29,Sai,,0,0,0,,made my body shiver in excitement\Nmore than ever before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.63,Sai,,0,0,0,,And I feel proud...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:10.25,Sai,,0,0,0,,that I could respond to you beyond\Nthe best of my own abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:14.80,Sai,,0,0,0,,Thank you... Touya Kouyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:19.97,Sai,,0,0,0,,Thank you... Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:28.31,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:34.51,Background,,0,0,0,,Master Touya prevented himself\Nfrom being cut here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:37.96,Background,,0,0,0,,You would think that he needs to make that move...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:40.08,Background,,0,0,0,,But if...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:41.36,Background,,0,0,0,,before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,he placed this stone in the corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,See? White has to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So he'll have gained more territory\Nthan he did during the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:20:00.76,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fad(334,334)}Note from translator: By placing the move in the corner, Black can kill White\Nunless White responds. Even if White responds, it leads to Seki, in which\Ncase White loses several stones worth of territory in the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:56.93,Background,,0,0,0,,In other words, if Black had played in\Nthe corner instead of connecting...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.59,Background,,0,0,0,,He would've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai, you would have lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:03.85,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.35,Sai,,0,0,0,,absolutely right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that, Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:18.66,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:28.91,Sai,,0,0,0,,I finally understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:33.09,Sai,,0,0,0,,God has...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:36.34,Sai,,0,0,0,,given me a millennium of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:38.34,Sai,,0,0,0,,simply to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:41.39,Sai,,0,0,0,,show Hikaru this match!
