Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:18.62,Background,,0,0,0,,The problem arises when White moves here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:21.04,Background,,0,0,0,,Should black play here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.15,0:22:25.34,Background,,0,0,0,,or here? Which is better?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.12,0:22:29.27,Background,,0,0,0,,If he plays here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.73,0:22:31.59,Background,,0,0,0,,White responds like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:36.13,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\an5\q2\fs20.5\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(417,0)\fscx850\t(0,400,1,\fscx99)\3c&H018307&\4c&H018307&\fscy110\bord1\shad0.5\pos(409,382)}It's easier for white to make eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.59,0:22:34.68,Background,,0,0,0,,and he can almost immediately get two eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:36.70,Background,,0,0,0,,White has plenty of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:41.39,Background,,0,0,0,,If he plays here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.01,0:22:43.89,Background,,0,0,0,,It may proceed like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.08,0:22:47.17,Background,,0,0,0,,and White won't be able to readily make two eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.87,0:22:49.43,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\an5\q2\fs20.5\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(459,0)\fscx900\t(0,430,1,\fscx99)\3c&H018307&\4c&H018307&\fscy110\bord1\shad0.5\pos(360,380)}It's tougher on white...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.41,0:22:49.08,Background,,0,0,0,,White has very little space.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If White comes into a place Black is strong in,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.05,0:22:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,respond aggressively so that White can't live easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:55.22,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs29\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(125,0)\3c&H1300EF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\fscx99\fscy100\bord2\shad1\move(305,265,305,304)}To be continued...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:57.37,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs29\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(0,0)\3c&H1300EF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\fscx99\fscy100\bord2\shad1\pos(305,304)}To be continued...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.57,0:23:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.48,0:23:03.98,Background,,0,0,0,,So you do know Sai after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:05.83,Background,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ogata...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.16,0:23:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you arrange that match...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,between Sai and Master Touya!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me play him, too!
